pawn, break as many cores as you can.<br></li><li> Earn points by distinguishing colorless cores from their symbols.<br></li><li> Earn points by distinguishing randomly colored cores from their symbols.<br></li><li> Earn points by breaking targeted cores.<br></li><li> Earn points by breaking the resulting explosives.</li></ul><strong>Take your place on the leaderboard.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Free Mode</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Keep blasting cores as many times as you want without any limitations.<br></li><li> Start free mode with the settings you want.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/BlastLaser_1.gif?t=1714931741\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Boost Impacts</strong></h2><strong>Can't pass a stage?</strong><br>Use boost impacts.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Mixer :</strong> Mixes all the cores.<br></li><li> <strong>Breaker :</strong> Affects object in the selected cell.<br></li><li> <strong>Horizontal Laser :</strong> Affects objects in the same row as the selected core.<br></li><li> <strong>Vertical Laser :</strong> Affects objects in the same column as the selected core.<br></li><li> <strong>Bomb :</strong> Affects objects within 1 unit of the selected core.<br></li><li> <strong>Dedector :</strong> Affects cores that are the same as the selected core type.<br></li><li> <strong>Double Laser :</strong> Affects objects in the same row and column as the selected core.<br></li><li> <strong>Large Laser :</strong> Affects objects in the same row and column within 1 unit of the selected core.<br></li><li> <strong>Large Bomb :</strong> Affects objects within 4 unit of the selected core.<br></li><li> <strong>Dedector-Laser :</strong> Converts cores that match the selected core type to lasers and detonates lasers.<br></li><li> <strong>Dedector-Bomb :</strong> Converts cores that match the selected core type to bombs and detonates bombs.<br></li><li> <s